and I don't believe it

47:22.131 --> 47:24.342
hate propaganda

47:26.678 --> 47:28.805
into your darkness

47:31.015 --> 47:33.184
to your hatred

47:35.645 --> 47:37.939
no, no, no, no

47:37.981 --> 47:40.066
no, no, no, no, no

47:40.108 --> 47:42.068
no, no, no, no

47:44.404 --> 47:46.656
I am electric

47:48.741 --> 47:50.952
for your destiny, no

47:53.162 --> 47:55.248
to children

47:55.290 --> 47:57.375
forced to run

47:57.417 --> 47:59.794
I'm not a minion

48:02.130 --> 48:04.507
no, no, no, no

48:04.549 --> 48:06.467
no, no, no, no, no

48:06.509 --> 48:08.720
no, no, no, no

